			<LI><P>The product and
			release information from your Internet browser (the so called &quot;user
			agent&quot;).</P>
		</UL>
		<P>This
		log file will be stored by KENIZEN in the standardized &quot;combined&quot;
		log file format for the Apache web server. KENIZEN will not store
