		legislation regarding the storage of data, Usersâ€™ IP addresses will
		be deleted or anonymized once they end their session on the KENIZEN
		Websites. Anonymization means that IP addresses are modified in such
		a way that specific personal and/or factual information cannot be
		attributed to a certain identified or identifiable person or can only
		be attributed by deploying a disproportionately large amount of time,
		effort and cost.</P>
		<P>KENIZEN
		uses the data from this log file in anonymous form without reference
		to your person for statistical purposes. In doing so, KENIZEN may
